# Color System

This app uses a strict two-color palette plus neutral grays. Do NOT introduce blue, sky, cyan, or other accent colors.

## Primary Colors

| Purpose | Color | Tailwind Classes |
|---------|-------|------------------|
| **Green (Emerald)** | Interactive elements, success states | `emerald-400`, `emerald-500`, `emerald-600` |
| **Purple (Violet)** | Navigation, links, info states | `violet-400`, `violet-500`, `violet-600` |
| **Red** | Errors only | `red-400`, `red-500`, `red-600` |
| **Amber** | Warnings only | `amber-400`, `amber-500` |

## Usage Guidelines

### Navigation & Tabs
- Active tab background: `bg-violet-600`
- All tabs use the same purple color when active

### Interactive Elements
- Toggles when ON: `peer-checked:bg-emerald-600`
- Primary buttons: `bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700`
- Focus borders: `focus:border-emerald-500`
- Active badges: `bg-emerald-600`

### Section Icons
- Use `text-violet-400` for section header icons
- Use `text-emerald-400` for status/activity indicators

### Links
- Text links: `text-violet-400 hover:text-violet-300`

### Toast Notifications
- Success: `emerald-500` (green border/progress)
- Error: `red-500` (red border/progress)
- Info: `violet-500` (purple border/progress)

## Forbidden Colors

Do NOT use these colors anywhere in the app:
- `sky-*` (blue)
- `blue-*`
- `cyan-*`
- `indigo-*` (use violet instead)
- `teal-*` (use emerald instead)

## Examples

```tsx
// ❌ BAD - Using blue
className="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300"
className="bg-sky-600"
className="focus:border-sky-500"

// ✅ GOOD - Using system colors
className="text-violet-400 hover:text-violet-300"  // for links
className="bg-violet-600"  // for navigation
className="focus:border-emerald-500"  // for interactive elements
```
